<plot>This short looks at New York City's Bowery district. It is here that the disenfranchised and downtrodden eke out their meager existence. We visit the Bowery Mission, where men are given food, a set of clean clothes, and a chance to become a useful member of society again.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?604848</url></doc>
